1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,000
1-Sahna: Buyurtma berish asoslari / Yapon tilida buyurtma berish

2
00:00:03,000 --> 00:00:05,533
Kechirasiz.

3
00:00:05,556 --> 00:00:08,789
Menyuni iltimos qilsam boʻladi mi?

4
00:00:08,812 --> 00:00:10,949
Ha.

5
00:00:10,973 --> 00:00:14,673
Mana, menyu.

6
00:00:14,696 --> 00:00:17,430
Rahmat.

7
00:00:17,453 --> 00:00:22,420
Shuningdek, suv berishingiz mumkinmi?

8
00:00:22,443 --> 00:00:25,143
Albatta.

9
00:00:25,166 --> 00:00:28,704
Hozir olib kelaman.

10
00:00:28,728 --> 00:00:31,161
Kechirasiz.

11
00:00:31,184 --> 00:00:34,287
Buyurtma berishni xohlayman.

12
00:00:34,311 --> 00:00:36,577
Ha.

13
00:00:36,600 --> 00:00:39,434
Nima buyurtma berasiz?

14
00:00:39,457 --> 00:00:43,090
Shuni menga ham bering.

15
00:00:43,113 --> 00:00:46,346
Gamburger seti, shundaymi?

16
00:00:46,369 --> 00:00:48,403
Ha.

17
00:00:48,426 --> 00:00:53,139
Shuningdek, tavsiya qiladigan narsangiz bormi?

18
00:00:53,163 --> 00:00:57,196
Mavsumiy sabzavotli salat juda mashhur.

19
00:00:57,219 --> 00:01:01,358
Unda, uni ham iltimos qilaman.

20
00:01:01,382 --> 00:01:04,015
Albatta.

21
00:01:04,038 --> 00:01:07,072
Hojatxona qayerda?

22
00:01:07,095 --> 00:01:10,595
U yerda, ichkarida.

23
00:01:10,618 --> 00:01:13,451
Rahmat.

24
00:01:13,474 --> 00:01:16,390
Kutib turganingiz uchun uzr.

25
00:01:16,413 --> 00:01:19,769
Buyurtmangiz tayyor.

26
00:01:19,793 --> 00:01:22,171
Kechirasiz.

27
00:01:22,195 --> 00:01:26,028
Buni olib ketishim mumkinmi?

28
00:01:26,051 --> 00:01:27,951
Ha.

29
00:01:27,974 --> 00:01:31,407
Paket olib kelaman.

30
00:01:31,430 --> 00:01:35,814
Boʻsh idishlarni olib ketishingiz mumkinmi?

31
00:01:35,838 --> 00:01:37,938
Ha.

32
00:01:37,961 --> 00:01:40,535
Albatta, olib ketaman.

33
00:01:40,558 --> 00:01:43,925
Hisobni iltimos qilaman.

34
00:01:43,948 --> 00:01:46,881
Kassaga boring.

35
00:01:46,904 --> 00:01:50,638
Jami 2500 yen.

36
00:01:50,661 --> 00:01:55,601
Doʻstlarim bilan alohida toʻlasak boʻladi mi?

37
00:01:55,624 --> 00:01:57,769
Ha.

38
00:01:57,793 --> 00:02:00,626
Hech qanday muammo yoʻq.

39
00:02:00,649 --> 00:02:03,649
2-Sahna: Kiyimni sinab koʻrish va almashtirish / Kiyimlarni sinash va almashtirish

40
00:02:03,649 --> 00:02:06,182
Kechirasiz.

41
00:02:06,205 --> 00:02:11,143
Bu koʻylakning boshqa rangi bormi?

42
00:02:11,167 --> 00:02:13,683
Ha.

43
00:02:13,706 --> 00:02:18,206
Oq va qora ranglari bor.

44
00:02:18,229 --> 00:02:22,823
Qora rangini sinab koʻrsam boʻladi mi?

45
00:02:22,847 --> 00:02:25,680
Ha.

46
00:02:25,703 --> 00:02:30,470
Sinab koʻrish xonasi mana u yerda.

47
00:02:30,493 --> 00:02:33,031
Aniq mos keldi!

48
00:02:33,054 --> 00:02:34,054
Buning yangi nusxasini olib keling.

49
00:02:34,077 --> 00:02:37,511
Albatta.

50
00:02:37,534 --> 00:02:41,520
Zaxiradagi mahsulotlarni tekshiraman.

51
00:02:41,543 --> 00:02:46,090
Arzonroq qilib bera olasizmi?

52
00:02:46,113 --> 00:02:47,113
Kechirasiz,

53
00:02:47,137 --> 00:02:51,775
Bu chegirma doirasida emas.

54
00:02:51,798 --> 00:02:54,698
Tushunarli.

55
00:02:54,721 --> 00:02:55,721
Shunda, buni sotib olaman.

56
00:02:55,744 --> 00:02:58,777
Rahmat.

57
00:02:58,800 --> 00:03:06,238
Doʻstimga sovgʻa qilish uchun, sovgʻa qilib oʻraysizmi?

58
00:03:06,261 --> 00:03:07,261
Ha,

59
00:03:07,284 --> 00:03:08,284
Bepul oʻrash kerakmi?

60
00:03:08,308 --> 00:03:12,008
Ha, iltimos.

61
00:03:12,031 --> 00:03:16,505
Plastik paket ham qoʻshamizmi?

62
00:03:16,528 --> 00:03:17,528
Yoʻq, ekologik sumkam bor, shuning uchun kerak emas.

63
00:03:17,551 --> 00:03:22,518
Toʻlovni qanday amalga oshirasiz?

64
00:03:22,541 --> 00:03:26,500
Kredit kartasi ishlatish mumkinmi?

65
00:03:26,523 --> 00:03:27,523
Ha,

66
00:03:27,546 --> 00:03:30,813
Foydalanishingiz mumkin.

67
00:03:30,836 --> 00:03:36,569
Agar oʻlchami mos kelmasa, qaytarish mumkinmi?

68
00:03:36,592 --> 00:03:37,592
Chek boʻlsa, bir hafta ichida qaytarishingiz mumkin.

69
00:03:37,615 --> 00:03:40,615
3-Sahna: Yoʻlning tirbandligi va mijozlarning soʻrovlariga javob berish

70
00:03:40,615 --> 00:03:43,054
Kechirasiz,

71
00:03:43,078 --> 00:03:47,111
Tokyo stansiyasiga olib boring.

72
00:03:47,134 --> 00:03:49,968
Albatta.

73
00:03:49,991 --> 00:03:50,991
Tokyo stansiyasining qaysi chiqishiga?

74
00:03:51,014 --> 00:03:54,931
Yaesu chiqishiga, iltimos.

75
00:03:54,955 --> 00:03:58,821
Xop, yoʻlga chiqamiz.

76
00:03:58,844 --> 00:04:02,711
Yoʻl tirband ekan, shundaymi?

77
00:04:02,734 --> 00:04:03,734
Ha, shunday.

78
00:04:03,757 --> 00:04:07,862
Oqshomlari har doim tirband boʻladi.

79
00:04:07,885 --> 00:04:08,885
Vaqtim yoʻq, shoshilishingiz mumkinmi?

80
00:04:08,908 --> 00:04:11,463
Tushunarli.

81
00:04:11,487 --> 00:04:15,263
Boshqa yoʻldan boraylikmi?

82
00:04:15,286 --> 00:04:18,519
Ha, iltimos.

83
00:04:18,542 --> 00:04:19,542
Yana besh daqiqada yetib kelamiz.

84
00:04:19,566 --> 00:04:22,364
Rahmat.

85
00:04:22,387 --> 00:04:23,387
A, shu doʻkon oldida toʻxtating.

86
00:04:23,410 --> 00:04:25,881
Shu yerda, shundaymi?

87
00:04:25,905 --> 00:04:26,905
2000 yen boʻladi.

88
00:04:26,928 --> 00:04:27,928
Transport IC kartasi bilan toʻlash mumkinmi?

89
00:04:27,951 --> 00:04:32,218
Ha, kartani tekkizing.

90
00:04:32,241 --> 00:04:35,756
Chek bering, iltimos.

91
00:04:35,779 --> 00:04:39,448
Ha, marhamat.

92
00:04:39,471 --> 00:04:42,783
Unutgan narsalaringizga eʼtibor bering.

93
00:04:42,806 --> 00:04:43,806
Kechirasiz,

94
00:04:43,830 --> 00:04:44,830
Yuklarim koʻp, bagajnikni ochib berishingiz mumkinmi?

95
00:04:44,853 --> 00:04:48,720
Ha, hozir ochaman.

96
00:04:48,743 --> 00:04:51,243
Rahmat.

97
00:04:51,265 --> 00:04:52,265
Xayrli safar, ehtiyot boʻling.

98
00:04:52,289 --> 00:04:55,289
4-Sahna: Mehmonxona roʻyxatdan oʻtish jarayoni

99
00:04:55,289 --> 00:04:57,789
Kechirasiz.

100
00:04:57,812 --> 00:05:01,445
Roʻyxatdan oʻtishni xohlayman.

101
00:05:01,468 --> 00:05:03,643
Ha.

102
00:05:03,667 --> 00:05:08,334
Bron qilgan ismingizni aytib bering.

103
00:05:08,357 --> 00:05:11,116
Smit.

104
00:05:11,139 --> 00:05:14,481
Uch kecha qolishni rejalashtirganman.

105
00:05:14,504 --> 00:05:17,460
Smit xonim/xoʻjayin, shundaymi?

106
00:05:17,483 --> 00:05:21,617
Bu yerga imzo cheking, iltimos.

107
00:05:21,640 --> 00:05:28,015
Xonaga kirishdan oldin, yuklarimni saqlab qoʻyishingiz mumkinmi?

108
00:05:28,038 --> 00:05:30,772
Albatta.

109
00:05:30,794 --> 00:05:34,228
Bu yerda saqlab qoʻyamiz.

110
00:05:34,251 --> 00:05:39,924
A, Wi-Fi parolini aytib bering.

111
00:05:39,948 --> 00:05:43,931
Xona kalitining orqa tomonida yozilgan.

112
00:05:43,954 --> 00:05:46,787
Rahmat.

113
00:05:46,810 --> 00:05:50,959
Nonushta nechanchidan boshlanadi?

114
00:05:50,982 --> 00:05:57,139
Ertalab soat yettidan birinchi qavatdagi restoranda nonushta tayyor boʻladi.

115
00:05:57,162 --> 00:06:00,029
Tushunarli.

116
00:06:00,052 --> 00:06:03,202
Xonangiz beshinchi qavatda boʻladi.

117
00:06:03,226 --> 00:06:05,770
Kechirasiz.

118
00:06:05,793 --> 00:06:09,126
Xonada issiq suv chiqmayapti.

119
00:06:09,149 --> 00:06:12,317
Kechirasiz.

120
00:06:12,340 --> 00:06:15,925
Tez orada tekshirib kelamiz.

121
00:06:15,949 --> 00:06:20,616
Yana bir sochiq bering.

122
00:06:20,638 --> 00:06:23,472
Albatta.

123
00:06:23,495 --> 00:06:26,264
Olib kelamiz.

124
00:06:26,287 --> 00:06:32,987
Agar issiq suv tuzatilmasa, xonani almashtirib berishingiz mumkinmi?

125
00:06:33,010 --> 00:06:36,925
Ha, albatta.

126
00:06:36,949 --> 00:06:41,708
Ertaga ertalab taksi chaqirib bering.

127
00:06:41,731 --> 00:06:44,365
Albatta.

128
00:06:44,389 --> 00:06:47,582
Nechanchida joʻnaysiz?

129
00:06:47,606 --> 00:06:51,382
Sakkizda bo'lsin, iltimos.

130
00:06:51,405 --> 00:06:54,405
5-Sahna: Kundalik suhbat asoslari / Asosiy yaponcha kundalik suhbatlar

131
00:06:54,405 --> 00:06:57,746
Katta, uzr, iltimos.

132
00:06:57,770 --> 00:07:01,645
Hozir vaqt bormi?

133
00:07:01,668 --> 00:07:05,812
Ha, nima bo'ldi?

134
00:07:05,835 --> 00:07:10,809
Ruchkani unutib qo'ydim, bir dona berib yuborasizmi?

135
00:07:10,833 --> 00:07:15,333
Marhamat, bu bilan foydalaning.

136
00:07:15,356 --> 00:07:18,023
Rahmat.

137
00:07:18,046 --> 00:07:23,279
Ushbu hujjatni qanday to'ldirishni bilmayapman.

138
00:07:23,302 --> 00:07:28,136
Bu yerga ism va manzil yozasiz.

139
00:07:28,159 --> 00:07:33,276
Kechirasiz, tez gapirganingiz uchun eshitolmadim.

140
00:07:33,299 --> 00:07:36,766
Iltimos, yana bir bor aytib bering.

141
00:07:36,789 --> 00:07:42,357
Bu yerga ism va manzilingizni yozing.

142
00:07:42,380 --> 00:07:45,114
Rahmat.

143
00:07:45,137 --> 00:07:49,814
Iltimos, sekinroq gapira olasizmi?

144
00:07:49,837 --> 00:07:54,424
Kechirasiz, endi e'tibor beraman.

145
00:07:54,448 --> 00:07:57,000
Yozib bo'ldim.

146
00:07:57,023 --> 00:08:00,598
Keyin nima qilish kerak?

147
00:08:00,621 --> 00:08:04,495
Buni nusxalab oling.

148
00:08:04,519 --> 00:08:09,064
Nusxa olish mashinasidan qanday foydalanishni o'rgatib yuboring.

149
00:08:09,087 --> 00:08:13,067
Faqat shu tugmani bosish kifoya.

150
00:08:13,091 --> 00:08:15,443
Tushunarli.

151
00:08:15,466 --> 00:08:20,499
A, chop etish to'xtab qoldi.

152
00:08:20,522 --> 00:08:24,089
Yordam berib yubora olasizmi?

153
00:08:24,113 --> 00:08:27,868
Qog'oz tiqilib qolgan bo'lishi mumkin.

154
00:08:27,892 --> 00:08:31,037
Biroz kutib turing.

155
00:08:31,060 --> 00:08:34,033
Yordam berdingiz, raxmat.

156
00:08:34,057 --> 00:08:37,390
Juda katta raxmat.

157
00:08:37,413 --> 00:08:42,530
Yo'q, boshqa tushunmovchiliklar bormi?

158
00:08:42,554 --> 00:08:46,335
Hozircha hammasi joyida.

159
00:08:46,359 --> 00:08:50,826
Ertaga dam olsam bo'ladimi?

160
00:08:50,849 --> 00:08:56,356
E, ertaga muhim yig'ilish bor-ku.

161
00:08:56,380 --> 00:08:59,380
6-Sahna: Rasmga olish va ruxsat so'rash suhbati / Suhbatda rasmga olish va ruxsat so'rash

162
00:08:59,380 --> 00:09:01,928
Kechirasiz.

163
00:09:01,951 --> 00:09:06,534
Rasmga olib yubora olasizmi?

164
00:09:06,558 --> 00:09:10,355
Ha, albatta.

165
00:09:10,378 --> 00:09:13,745
Kamerani berib yuboring.

166
00:09:13,768 --> 00:09:17,753
Bu tugmani bosing.

167
00:09:17,777 --> 00:09:20,158
Ha.

168
00:09:20,181 --> 00:09:23,348
Cheese!

169
00:09:23,372 --> 00:09:27,451
Yana bitta rasmga olamizmi?

170
00:09:27,474 --> 00:09:30,049
Rahmat.

171
00:09:30,073 --> 00:09:35,206
Birga rasmga tushsak bo'ladimi?

172
00:09:35,229 --> 00:09:38,422
Men bilanmi?

173
00:09:38,446 --> 00:09:42,512
Ha, xursandman.

174
00:09:42,535 --> 00:09:45,969
Yodgorlik bo'ldi.

175
00:09:45,992 --> 00:09:51,512
U yerda, qal'aga kirsam bo'ladimi?

176
00:09:51,535 --> 00:09:56,108
U yerga kirish uchun chipta kerak.

177
00:09:56,131 --> 00:10:00,165
Chiptani qayerdan sotib olish mumkin?

178
00:10:00,188 --> 00:10:05,093
U yerda oq bino ichida sotib olishingiz mumkin.

179
00:10:05,116 --> 00:10:09,434
Inglizcha buklet berib yuborasizmi?

180
00:10:09,457 --> 00:10:12,957
Qabulxonada bor.

181
00:10:12,980 --> 00:10:17,332
Yaponcha gid bormi?

182
00:10:17,356 --> 00:10:21,822
Soat o'ndan boshlab bepul tur mavjud.

183
00:10:21,845 --> 00:10:25,412
Ishtirok etmoqchiman.

184
00:10:25,435 --> 00:10:31,303
Yukim og'ir, shkaf (locker) bormi?

185
00:10:31,327 --> 00:10:35,560
Vokzal yaqinida joylashgan.

186
00:10:35,583 --> 00:10:39,766
Bu yer necha vaqtgacha ochiq?

187
00:10:39,790 --> 00:10:43,157
Beshgacha ochiq.

188
00:10:43,180 --> 00:10:45,857
Tushunarli.

189
00:10:45,880 --> 00:10:50,813
Skameykada tushlik qilsam bo‘ladimi?

190
00:10:50,836 --> 00:10:53,136
Ha.

191
00:10:53,159 --> 00:10:56,992
Ovqatlanish erkin.

192
00:10:57,015 --> 00:11:00,015
7-SAHNA: SHIFOXONA TOPISH VA ALAMATLARNI TAVSIFLASH

193
00:11:00,015 --> 00:11:02,720
Kechirasiz.

194
00:11:02,743 --> 00:11:07,043
Yaqin atrofdagi shifoxonani aytib bera olasizmi?

195
00:11:07,066 --> 00:11:09,933
Nima bo‘ldi?

196
00:11:09,957 --> 00:11:13,635
Yuzingiz rangi yomon ko‘rinib turibdi.

197
00:11:13,658 --> 00:11:18,092
Kecha-kunduz boshim og‘riyapti.

198
00:11:18,115 --> 00:11:21,233
Isitmangiz ham bormi?

199
00:11:21,256 --> 00:11:25,638
Ha, biroz isitma bor.

200
00:11:25,662 --> 00:11:29,095
Bu juda yomon ekan.

201
00:11:29,118 --> 00:11:32,230
Ichki kasalliklar bo‘limiga boring.

202
00:11:32,254 --> 00:11:36,921
Inglizcha gaplasha oladigan shifokor bormi?

203
00:11:36,944 --> 00:11:42,112
Vokzal oldidagi klinikada inglizcha tushunishadi.

204
00:11:42,135 --> 00:11:44,841
Rahmat.

205
00:11:44,864 --> 00:11:48,097
U yerga borib ko‘rayapman.

206
00:11:48,120 --> 00:11:51,075
Ehtiyot bo‘ling.

207
00:11:51,099 --> 00:11:53,766
Kechirasiz.

208
00:11:53,789 --> 00:11:56,822
Ko‘rib chiqib bera olasizmi?

209
00:11:56,845 --> 00:11:59,482
Birinchi marta kelayapsizmi?

210
00:11:59,506 --> 00:12:03,039
Sug‘urta guvo‘nomasini ko‘rsating.

211
00:12:03,062 --> 00:12:07,129
Yapon sug‘urta guvo‘nomasidan foydalanishim mumkinmi?

212
00:12:07,152 --> 00:12:10,618
Ha, foydalanishingiz mumkin.

213
00:12:10,641 --> 00:12:13,880
Anketa to‘ldiring.

214
00:12:13,903 --> 00:12:19,237
Holsizim yomon, biroz dam olishga ruxsat bering.

215
00:12:19,260 --> 00:12:23,244
Shu karavotda yotib turing.

216
00:12:23,267 --> 00:12:30,100
Doktor, ishga bormayman, shuning uchun kasallik varaqasi yozib bering.

217
00:12:30,123 --> 00:12:32,390
Tushunarli.

218
00:12:32,413 --> 00:12:35,772
Dori yozib beraman.

219
00:12:35,796 --> 00:12:39,671
Og‘riqni bosuvchi dori bering.

220
00:12:39,694 --> 00:12:43,796
Har bir ovqattan keyin iching.

221
00:12:43,820 --> 00:12:46,453
Tezroq sog‘aying.

222
00:12:46,476 --> 00:12:49,643
Rahmat.

223
00:12:49,666 --> 00:12:52,666
8-SAHNA: SUMKANGIZ O‘G‘IRLANGANDA QILINADIGANLAR

224
00:12:52,666 --> 00:12:56,536
Kechirasiz, yordam bering!

225
00:12:56,559 --> 00:12:57,559
Nima bo‘ldi?

226
00:12:57,582 --> 00:13:00,249
Tinchlaning.

227
00:13:00,272 --> 00:13:04,505
Sumkamni o‘g‘irlab ketishdi.

228
00:13:04,528 --> 00:13:05,528
Nima?!

229
00:13:05,552 --> 00:13:08,785
Bu juda yomon holat.

230
00:13:08,808 --> 00:13:09,808
Darhol politsiyani chaqiring.

231
00:13:09,831 --> 00:13:14,164
Telefon ham sumkamda edi.

232
00:13:14,187 --> 00:13:17,487
Telefoningizdan foydalanishim mumkinmi?

233
00:13:17,510 --> 00:13:21,344
Ha, marhamat.

234
00:13:21,367 --> 00:13:22,367
110 raqamiga qo‘ng‘iroq qiling.

235
00:13:22,390 --> 00:13:27,423
Allo, sumkamni o‘g‘irlab ketishdi.

236
00:13:27,446 --> 00:13:30,746
Politsiya, shundaymi?

237
00:13:30,769 --> 00:13:31,769
Qayerda o‘g‘irlangan?

238
00:13:31,792 --> 00:13:32,792
Vokzal hojatxonasiga qo‘yib ketgan edim, qaytib kelganimda yo‘q edi.

239
00:13:32,816 --> 00:13:33,816
Sumkangizda nimalar bor edi?

240
00:13:33,839 --> 00:13:38,552
Hamyon va pasportim bor edi.

241
00:13:38,575 --> 00:13:39,575
Kredit kartangiz ham bor edi-mi?

242
00:13:39,598 --> 00:13:40,598
Ha. Kartani darhol to‘xtatib qo‘ying.

243
00:13:40,622 --> 00:13:46,591
Karta kompaniyasiga o‘zingiz aloqaga chiqib, to‘xtatib qo‘ying.

244
00:13:46,614 --> 00:13:49,559
Tushunarli.

245
00:13:49,582 --> 00:13:50,582
Yana, Yaponiya elchixonasi qayerda?

246
00:13:50,606 --> 00:13:55,395
Pasportni qayta chiqarish kerak, shundaymi?

247
00:13:55,418 --> 00:13:58,851
Xarita beraman.

248
00:13:58,874 --> 00:13:59,874
Uy kaliti ham sumkamda, xonaga kira olmayapman.

249
00:13:59,898 --> 00:14:00,898
Uy egasining telefon raqamini aytib bering.

250
00:14:00,921 --> 00:14:01,921
Smartfonim yo‘q, raqamni bilmayman.

251
00:14:01,944 --> 00:14:05,286
Qiyin bo‘lib qoldi, rostdan.

252
00:14:05,309 --> 00:14:09,107
Oilamga qo‘ng‘iroq qilishim kerak.

253
00:14:09,131 --> 00:14:14,466
Ha, bu telefondan foydalaning.

254
00:14:14,489 --> 00:14:17,489
9-Sahna: Do‘stlar bilan uchrashuv rejalashtirish

255
00:14:17,489 --> 00:14:23,756
Aytgin, navbatdagi dam olish kunimizda birga chiqamizmi?

256
00:14:23,779 --> 00:14:26,018
Yaxshi fikr!

257
00:14:26,041 --> 00:14:27,041
Qayerga boramiz?

258
00:14:27,064 --> 00:14:28,064
Yangi kafe ochilgan, u yerga borib ko‘ramiz.

259
00:14:28,087 --> 00:14:30,721
Ma‘qul.

260
00:14:30,744 --> 00:14:31,744
Unda, LINE raqamingni ber.

261
00:14:31,767 --> 00:14:32,767
Ha.

262
00:14:32,790 --> 00:14:37,058
QR-kodni skanerla.

263
00:14:37,082 --> 00:14:40,115
Ro‘yxatdan o‘tdim.

264
00:14:40,138 --> 00:14:43,675
Keyinroq tafsilotlarni yuboraman.

265
00:14:43,699 --> 00:14:44,699
Kechirasiz.

266
00:14:44,722 --> 00:14:45,722
Biroz kutib turing.

267
00:14:45,745 --> 00:14:49,379
Poyafzalimning bog‘ichini bog‘lay olmayapman.

268
00:14:49,402 --> 00:14:52,735
Shoshilmang, sekinroq qila olasan.

269
00:14:52,758 --> 00:14:56,391
Tomoqim quridi.

270
00:14:56,414 --> 00:14:57,414
Kompiniya (do‘konga) to‘xtab o‘tsak bo‘ladimi?

271
00:14:57,438 --> 00:15:00,188
Ha.

272
00:15:00,211 --> 00:15:05,200
A, shu bilan birga pul ham qarz berolmaysizmi?

273
00:15:05,223 --> 00:15:06,223
Eh, qancha kerak?

274
00:15:06,246 --> 00:15:07,246
Faqat 500 yen.

275
00:15:07,269 --> 00:15:11,028
Hamyonimni unutib qo‘ydim.

276
00:15:11,052 --> 00:15:13,885
Bo‘lmasa ham bo‘ladi-ku.

277
00:15:13,908 --> 00:15:14,908
Mana, 500 yen.

278
00:15:14,931 --> 00:15:17,365
Rahmat.

279
00:15:17,388 --> 00:15:21,374
Ertaga albatta qaytarib beraman.

280
00:15:21,397 --> 00:15:22,397
Bu pirog nihoyatda mazali ekan!

281
00:15:22,421 --> 00:15:23,421
Rostdanmi?

282
00:15:23,444 --> 00:15:24,444
Menga ham bir tishlab ber.

283
00:15:24,467 --> 00:15:27,062
Yaxshi.

284
00:15:27,085 --> 00:15:30,352
Mana, ovqatlan.

285
00:15:30,375 --> 00:15:31,375
Shirin-chuchuk!

286
00:15:31,398 --> 00:15:32,398
Mening blinchiklarimni ham tatib ko‘rasanmi?

287
00:15:32,421 --> 00:15:33,421
Tatib ko‘raman! A, suratni ham yubor.

288
00:15:33,445 --> 00:15:35,843
Ha.

289
00:15:35,866 --> 00:15:39,370
Hozir LINE orqali yubordim.

290
00:15:39,393 --> 00:15:41,659
Rahmat.

291
00:15:41,682 --> 00:15:42,682
Bu do‘kon haqida boshqa hech kimga aytmang.

292
00:15:42,706 --> 00:15:44,972
Ma‘qul.

293
00:15:44,995 --> 00:15:48,562
Faqat ikkimizning sirimiz bo‘lsin.

294
00:15:48,585 --> 00:15:51,585
10-Sahna: Yig‘ilishni tayyorlash va tasdiqlash

295
00:15:51,585 --> 00:15:54,618
Mehnatingiz uchun rahmat.

296
00:15:54,641 --> 00:15:57,908
Ovozingiz eshitilayapti?

297
00:15:57,931 --> 00:16:01,690
Ha, eshitilayapti.

298
00:16:01,713 --> 00:16:03,904
Kechirasiz,

299
00:16:03,928 --> 00:16:07,647
Mikrofonni yoqing, iltimos.

300
00:16:07,670 --> 00:16:10,737
A, kechirasiz.

301
00:16:10,760 --> 00:16:13,919
Hozir yoqdim.

302
00:16:13,943 --> 00:16:17,009
Muammo yoʻq.

303
00:16:17,032 --> 00:16:20,999
Endi, yigʻilishni boshlaymiz.

304
00:16:21,022 --> 00:16:26,089
Bu haftaning savdo maʼlumotlariga qarang.

305
00:16:26,112 --> 00:16:31,101
Ekraningizni ulashingiz mumkinmi?

306
00:16:31,124 --> 00:16:35,163
Ha, biroz kutib turing.

307
00:16:35,187 --> 00:16:38,420
Bunday qanday?

308
00:16:38,443 --> 00:16:42,276
Hali koʻrinmayapti.

309
00:16:42,299 --> 00:16:46,937
Qaytadan ulanib koʻrsam boʻladi mi?

310
00:16:46,960 --> 00:16:49,694
Tushunarli.

311
00:16:49,717 --> 00:16:52,386
Kutyapman.

312
00:16:52,409 --> 00:16:55,275
Kutib turdingiz, uzr.

313
00:16:55,298 --> 00:17:00,565
A, ovozingiz biroz uzoqda eshitilmoqda.

314
00:17:00,588 --> 00:17:03,255
Rostdanmi?

315
00:17:03,278 --> 00:17:08,657
Iltimos, biroz balandroq gapiring.

316
00:17:08,681 --> 00:17:12,416
Mikrofonni sinab koʻrmoqdaman.

317
00:17:12,439 --> 00:17:14,814
Qanday endi?

318
00:17:14,838 --> 00:17:19,551
Ha, endi juda yaxshi.

319
00:17:19,575 --> 00:17:22,342
Yaxshi boʻldi.

320
00:17:22,365 --> 00:17:26,964
Ushbu yigʻilishni yozib olsam boʻladi mi?

321
00:17:26,987 --> 00:17:31,258
Ha, muammo yoʻq.

322
00:17:31,281 --> 00:17:36,619
Muhim URL manzillarni chatga yozib qoʻying.

323
00:17:36,643 --> 00:17:40,914
Hozir havolani yubordim.

324
00:17:40,937 --> 00:17:43,970
Tasdiqladim.

325
00:17:43,993 --> 00:17:48,775
Batafsil maʼlumotni keyinroq elektron pochtaga yuboring.

326
00:17:48,798 --> 00:17:51,732
Tushunarli.

327
00:17:51,755 --> 00:17:56,488
Yigʻilish bayonnomasi bilan birga yuboraman.

328
00:17:56,511 --> 00:17:59,544
Iltimos.